{"lemma":"مُسافِرٌ","slug":"مُسافِرٌ","root":"س.ف.ر","root_slug":"س-ف-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ف-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19954"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"traveller"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb سَافَرَ (sāfara)."},"ipa":["/mu.saː.fir/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19954","headword_ar":"مُسَافِرٌ","root":"sfr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"travelling; a traveller; a wayfarer;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAfirN","text_ar":"سَافِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, * K;) which latter is [said to be] not a part. n., but [a possessive epithet] meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw","text_ar":"ذُو"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safarK","text_ar":"سَفَرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) having no verb belonging to it (M, K) that we have seen; (M;) or it is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safara","text_ar":"سَفَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going forth on a journey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musaAfiruwna","text_ar":"مُسَافِرُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and of the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suf~aArN","text_ar":"سُفَّارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asofaArN","text_ar":"اَسْفَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suf~arN","text_ar":"سُفَّرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and you also say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomN saAfirapN","text_ar":"قَوْمٌ سَافِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAfirN","text_ar":"سَافِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, * M, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomN saforN","text_ar":"قَوْمٌ سَفْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Msb, K,) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saforN","text_ar":"سَفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being a quasi-pl. n.,] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHobN","text_ar":"صَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in relation to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAHibo","text_ar":"صَاحِبْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Mgh, Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saforN","text_ar":"سَفْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used as a sing., (M, K,) being originally an inf. n. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musaAfirapN","text_ar":"مُسَافِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used by Zuheyr as a name for"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wild"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","S","Msb","A","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%85%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%B1/","headword_ar":"مسافر","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23646#ac117e","body_html":"<span>المسافر: هو من قصد سيرًا وسطًا ثلاثة أيام ولياليها، وفارق بيوت بلده.</span>"}]}}